  "description": {
    "en": "Herbal preparation derived from Buguzhi. Buguzhi is an acrid, bitter herb that is very warming in nature. It enters the kidney and spleen meridians, and is thus useful for tonifying the kidneys and fortifying the yang, consolidating the jing..."
